# NeNe Concierge

Self-hosted chat scenario platform on NENE2 (PHP 8.4).

## What it is
- Visual scenario editor (React flow canvas) + AI scenario authoring via MCP/API
- Embed widget for conversion-focused chat on any same-origin page
- Action engine: email, Slack, Chatwork, external HTTP from scenario nodes
- Dual deployment: Tier A (shared hosting) and Tier B (Docker/VPS)

## Key rules
- Issue-driven. No code/doc/config change without a GitHub Issue.
- No direct commits to `main`. Branch → PR → merge.
- Conventional Commits: `type(scope): 日本語説明 (#issue)`
- Handler → UseCase → Repository layering. No SQL in handlers.
- MCP tools: operator/AI only. Never expose to embed widget visitors.
- No DB access for AI/MCP tools. HTTP boundaries only.
- `declare(strict_types=1)` in every PHP file.

